From 3cb43ef97486f1022f268db7002590faf5eb60f5 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Anan Almasri <anan@ananalmasri.com>
Date: Wed, 22 Jul 2026 11:55:45 -0400
Subject: [PATCH] Promote Blueprint Eternity to the public homepage

- Add /legacy route that preserves the original marketing landing page.
- Make / render the six-sprint Blueprint Eternity demo (was /demo).
- Add scripts/deploy.sh so the VPS can pull, build, restart, and smoke test in one step.
- Promote chat JSON-envelope fix to server.js and add client-side normalization in src/lib/demo/chatResponse.ts.
- Add suggested-answer and follow-up question chips; question chips focus the composer instead of echoing the prompt back to n8n.
- Update README.md with the new routes and the VPS deploy/rollback workflow.
